            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EHow%20sad%20it%20is%20to%20see%20a%20person%20move%20from%20having%20a%20tender%20heart%20and%20complete%20trust%20in%20God%20to%20having%20a%20cold%2C%20hard%20heart%20and%20an%20analytical%20mind%20that%20calculates%20every%20move.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EUnfortunately%2C%20that%20is%20just%20what%20happened%20to%20Asa.%20%20He%20began%20his%20reign%20with%20a%20mighty%20victory%2C%20totally%20relying%20upon%20the%20Lord%20to%20defeat%20the%20Ethiopians.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20his%20reign%2C%20however%2C%20when%20he%20had%20grown%20old%20and%20was%20no%20longer%20childlike%20in%20his%20faith%2C%20he%20hired%20mercenary%20soldiers%20to%20fight%20his%20battles.%20The%20prophet%20rebuked%20him%20for%20his%20unbelief%2C%20reminding%20him%20that%20%22the%20eyes%20of%20the%20Lord%20search%20the%20whole%20earth%20in%20order%20to%20strengthen%20those%20whose%20hearts%20are%20fully%20committed%20to%20him%22%20(2%20Chronicles%2016%3A9).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAsa's%20unbelieving%20attitude%20was%20also%20evident%20in%20his%20latter%20years%20when%20he%20%22developed%20a%20serious%20foot%20disease.%20Even%20when%20the%20disease%20became%20life%20threatening%2C%20he%20did%20not%20seek%20the%20Lord's%20help%20but%20sought%20help%20only%20from%20his%20physicians.%20So%20he%20died%20in%20the%20forty-first%20year%20of%20his%20reign%22%20(2%20Chronicles%2016%3A12-13).%20How%20far%20Asa%20had%20strayed%20from%20the%20time%20when%20the%20whole%20nation%20sought%20the%20Lord%20and%20God%20gave%20him%20%22rest%20from%20his%20enemies%22%20(2%20Chronicles%2014%3A6)!%20He%20now%20focused%20his%20hope%20on%20the%20efforts%20of%20man%20rather%20than%20the%20power%20of%20God.%20Asa%20was%20not%20wrong%20to%20seek%20the%20help%20of%20physicians%2C%20but%20he%20did%20err%20in%20placing%20his%20trust%20in%20them%20rather%20than%20in%20the%20Lord.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELet%20us%20purpose%20to%20stay%20simple%2C%20trusting%2C%20and%20childlike%20in%20total%20dependence%20upon%20God%20for%20all%20our%20days.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "2Chr.14:1-16:14",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Chronicles%2014%3A1-16%3A14%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_1%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Chronicles%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EEarly%20Years%20of%20Asa%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Reign%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E14%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Verse%26%23xA0%3B14%3A1%20is%20numbered%2013%3A23%20in%20Hebrew%20text.%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Abijah%20died%2C%20he%20was%20buried%20in%20the%20City%20of%20David.%20Then%20his%20son%20Asa%20became%20the%20next%20king.%20There%20was%20peace%20in%20the%20land%20for%20ten%20years.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_2%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E14%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Verses%2014%3A2-15%20are%20numbered%2014%3A1-14%20in%20Hebrew%20text.%3C%2Fspan%3EAsa%20did%20what%20was%20pleasing%20and%20good%20in%20the%20sight%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20his%20God.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_3%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20removed%20the%20foreign%20altars%20and%20the%20pagan%20shrines.%20He%20smashed%20the%20sacred%20pillars%20and%20cut%20down%20the%20Asherah%20poles.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_4%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20commanded%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%20to%20seek%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20their%20ancestors%2C%20and%20to%20obey%20his%20law%20and%20his%20commands.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_5%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAsa%20also%20removed%20the%20pagan%20shrines%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20incense%20altars%20from%20every%20one%20of%20Judah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20towns.%20So%20Asa%26%23x2019%3Bs%20kingdom%20enjoyed%20a%20period%20of%20peace.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_6%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EDuring%20those%20peaceful%20years%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20build%20up%20the%20fortified%20towns%20throughout%20Judah.%20No%20one%20tried%20to%20make%20war%20against%20him%20at%20this%20time%2C%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20giving%20him%20rest%20from%20his%20enemies.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_7%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EAsa%20told%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLet%20us%20build%20towns%20and%20fortify%20them%20with%20walls%2C%20towers%2C%20gates%2C%20and%20bars.%20The%20land%20is%20still%20ours%20because%20we%20sought%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%2C%20and%20he%20has%20given%20us%20peace%20on%20every%20side.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20they%20went%20ahead%20with%20these%20projects%20and%20brought%20them%20to%20completion.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_8%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EKing%20Asa%20had%20an%20army%20of%20300%2C000%20warriors%20from%20the%20tribe%20of%20Judah%2C%20armed%20with%20large%20shields%20and%20spears.%20He%20also%20had%20an%20army%20of%20280%2C000%20warriors%20from%20the%20tribe%20of%20Benjamin%2C%20armed%20with%20small%20shields%20and%20bows.%20Both%20armies%20were%20composed%20of%20well-trained%20fighting%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_9%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EOnce%20an%20Ethiopian%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E14%3A9a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ea%20Cushite.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20named%20Zerah%20attacked%20Judah%20with%20an%20army%20of%201%2C000%2C000%20men%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E14%3A9b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ean%20army%20of%20thousands%20and%20thousands%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Ean%20army%20of%20a%20thousand%20thousands.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20300%26%23xA0%3Bchariots.%20They%20advanced%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Mareshah%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_10%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3Eso%20Asa%20deployed%20his%20armies%20for%20battle%20in%20the%20valley%20north%20of%20Mareshah.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E14%3A10%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Evalley%20of%20Zephathah%20near%20Mareshah.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_11%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Asa%20cried%20out%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20his%20God%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20no%20one%20but%20you%20can%20help%20the%20powerless%20against%20the%20mighty!%20Help%20us%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%2C%20for%20we%20trust%20in%20you%20alone.%20It%20is%20in%20your%20name%20that%20we%20have%20come%20against%20this%20vast%20horde.%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20you%20are%20our%20God%3B%20do%20not%20let%20mere%20men%20prevail%20against%20you!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_12%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20defeated%20the%20Ethiopians%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E14%3A12%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ECushites%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2014%3A13.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Asa%20and%20the%20army%20of%20Judah%2C%20and%20the%20enemy%20fled.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_13%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EAsa%20and%20his%20army%20pursued%20them%20as%20far%20as%20Gerar%2C%20and%20so%20many%20Ethiopians%20fell%20that%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20rally.%20They%20were%20destroyed%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20his%20army%2C%20and%20the%20army%20of%20Judah%20carried%20off%20a%20vast%20amount%20of%20plunder.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_14%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EWhile%20they%20were%20at%20Gerar%2C%20they%20attacked%20all%20the%20towns%20in%20that%20area%2C%20and%20terror%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20came%20upon%20the%20people%20there.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20a%20vast%20amount%20of%20plunder%20was%20taken%20from%20these%20towns%2C%20too.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_14_15%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20also%20attacked%20the%20camps%20of%20herdsmen%20and%20captured%20many%20sheep%2C%20goats%2C%20and%20camels%20before%20finally%20returning%20to%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_15_1%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Chronicles%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EAsa%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Religious%20Reforms%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20Spirit%20of%20God%20came%20upon%20Azariah%20son%20of%20Oded%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_15_2%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20he%20went%20out%20to%20meet%20King%20Asa%20as%20he%20was%20returning%20from%20the%20battle.%20%26%23x201C%3BListen%20to%20me%2C%20Asa!%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20shouted.%20%26%23x201C%3BListen%2C%20all%20you%20people%20of%20Judah%20and%20Benjamin!%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20stay%20with%20you%20as%20long%20as%20you%20stay%20with%20him!%20Whenever%20you%20seek%20him%2C%20you%20will%20find%20him.%20But%20if%20you%20abandon%20him%2C%20he%20will%20abandon%20you.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_15_3%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%20Israel%20was%20without%20the%20true%20God%2C%20without%20a%20priest%20to%20teach%20them%2C%20and%20without%20the%20Law%20to%20instruct%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_15_4%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20